lead_paragraph: The Swiss National Bank kept its interest rates at record lows on Thursday, citing increased global uncertainty in the wake of the U.S. presidential election and upcoming votes across Europe.

headline.main: Swiss Keep Rates on Hold Amid Political Uncertainty
headline.print_headline: Swiss Keep Rates on Hold Amid Political Uncertainty
